&lt;li&gt;Play a central operational role within the communications team — helping manage workflows, maintain internal systems, and keep concurrent projects on track in a fast-moving, high-volume environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to publicity strategy across Semafor&#39;s editorial verticals and business priorities, including pitching, writing press releases, conducting research, and developing communications campaigns&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
