&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated experience leading complex integrations across multiple tools and data systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Technical fluency to work credibly alongside engineers and make informed architecture decisions. You can prototype, debug, and get your hands dirty&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience applying AI tools (LLMs, agents, workflow automation) to real operational problems, not as side projects or experiments, but as shipped solutions that changed how a team works&lt;/li&gt;
