&lt;li&gt;Experience in media, events, or a similarly fast-moving, relationship-driven industry a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working knowledge of no-code/low-code tools like Airtable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The base salary for this position ranges from &lt;strong&gt;$150,000 - $175,000&lt;/strong&gt; per year, plus performance-based bonus eligibility. Individual compensation varies based on job-related factors, including business needs, experience, level of responsibility, and qualifications.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Additional Job Details:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This position is based in our New York City office with a hybrid work arrangement (in-office Monday-Thursday, remote Friday).&amp;nbsp; Candidates must be authorized to work in the United States.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Additional job details&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

