&lt;li&gt;Identify, research, and target compelling, diverse speakers and drive outreach with persistence, creativity, and diplomacy to secure participation from high-profile and hard-to-reach individuals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage all stages of the speaker process — from research and invitations to confirmations, pre-event briefings, and day-of management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the development of briefing materials for Semafor’s editorial moderators, including logistical details and suggested questions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the lead speaker wrangler and show manager during events, managing arrival schedules, green rooms, AV preparations, and stage flow.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
