&lt;li&gt;A Bachelor&#39;s degree is required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;7+ years in broadcast journalism, event content or programming development, or related fields.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated experience managing complex editorial programs across dozens of speakers and sessions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional interpersonal skills and proven ability to engage confidently with senior-level executives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Outstanding verbal and written communication, including the ability to craft compelling invitations and executive briefs.&lt;/li&gt;
