&lt;li&gt;Write agenda-setting stories that situate individual company or policy decisions in the larger context of capital accumulation, geopolitical competition, and technological transformation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Semafor journalists across business, finance, politics, and international coverage to produce breakout cross-beat stories&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to Semafor&#39;s live journalism, including news-breaking, on-record panels with senior business and political figures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
